title: Hungary Industrial Production MoM
description: Industrial Production in Hungary increased 1.60 percent in September of 2022 over the previous month. Industrial Production Mom in Hungary averaged 0.48 percent from 1994 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 17.90 percent in May of 2020 and a record low of -29.70 percent in April of 2020. This page provides the latest reported value for - Hungary Industrial Production MoM - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Hungarian Central Statistical Office
